# Runtime artifacts generated when the harness runs under HOME=<scenario>.
# The committed per-scenario tree is:
#   <scenario>/input.env
#   <scenario>/golden-terminal.txt
#   <scenario>/golden-json.txt
#   <scenario>/.local/share/cctally/stats.db
#   <scenario>/.local/share/cctally/cache.db
# Anything else SQLite or the CLI writes during a run is ignored so the
# working tree stays clean after `build-diff-fixtures.py` and any
# subsequent harness invocation.
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.log
.local/share/cctally/config.json
.local/share/cctally/logs/
.local/share/cctally/cache.db*.lock
